{"id": "ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0", "rating": 4.8, "userRatingCount": 35, "displayName": {"text": "Onigiri Time", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25weFJrWmxWbk5WWDNvNU1IQjFTWGx6U0hWU2IyYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Omg the onigiri here is amazing!! They're giant and so filling. The wasabi cream is such a great accent. But the onigiri on its own is also delicious!!\n\nI got the crab and the chicken. I devoured the crab first and was too full to eat the chicken so that'll be my meal later today.\n\nWorth every penny and the packaging is not only adorable it's super functional! You have to check these guys out!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Omg the onigiri here is amazing!! They're giant and so filling. The wasabi cream is such a great accent. But the onigiri on its own is also delicious!!\n\nI got the crab and the chicken. I devoured the crab first and was too full to eat the chicken so that'll be my meal later today.\n\nWorth every penny and the packaging is not only adorable it's super functional! You have to check these guys out!!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Candie Brown", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104671398777024920947/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVNc9d8XSjFmvwmmT5lmKM24V729_2eqZA_zSsecPBCr6hjtSBeNA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-26T03:20:41.026806480Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25weFJrWmxWbk5WWDNvNU1IQjFTWGx6U0hWU2IyYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25weFJrWmxWbk5WWDNvNU1IQjFTWGx6U0hWU2IyYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3000fe7b0a1:0xbdc0bff616ef6394"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0Uk5FbElVbXB6ZVY5QmJGSmFiVlpUT1doeE5HYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "A wonderful takeaway package encompasses a Japanese-style rice ball filled with delicious ingredients, packed with traditional flavors. Most excited for the availability of Onigiri, especially from a cart; this is a must-try for everyone. Items are fresh and packaged slightly warm. Sized generously, each can be a meal on its own. Unfortunately, the flavors available always get me to order at least a couple. The inspiration is awesome, and the owner has a level of excitement that will probably turn into a cult following. I am hoping the flavors expand and the value continues. (Hint: Smoked Salmon, Salted Cod/Salmon, or possibly an Egg alternative)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "A wonderful takeaway package encompasses a Japanese-style rice ball filled with delicious ingredients, packed with traditional flavors. Most excited for the availability of Onigiri, especially from a cart; this is a must-try for everyone. Items are fresh and packaged slightly warm. Sized generously, each can be a meal on its own. Unfortunately, the flavors available always get me to order at least a couple. The inspiration is awesome, and the owner has a level of excitement that will probably turn into a cult following. I am hoping the flavors expand and the value continues. (Hint: Smoked Salmon, Salted Cod/Salmon, or possibly an Egg alternative)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "James", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102595820736418415381/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWDzB-goiGp8RsQXzHbCLbwVRwriO8Ot44aYu5XQYqbbLeX5BY=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-25T06:09:49.683418834Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0Uk5FbElVbXB6ZVY5QmJGSmFiVlpUT1doeE5HYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t0Uk5FbElVbXB6ZVY5QmJGSmFiVlpUT1doeE5HYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3000fe7b0a1:0xbdc0bff616ef6394"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOVE1XOWxkbkU0VmpnM1pGUjNUa0ZVTTBoUVprRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The biggest and best onigiri in the world! 🍙\n\nThe owner Tony is the nicest human, and makes you feel like a regular on day one.\n\nMy favorite is the blue crab, but they have rotating specials that are so fun to try. Two onigiris are usually more than enough for a filling lunch for me. The half white rice and half Korean purple rice is so awesome and the rice is so fresh (not fridge stale like in the Asian grocery stores). And the way they wrap up the bags with string is so cool!\n\nCheck out their Instagram for up to date hours or if they've sold out for the day. (They also do fun TikTok trends 😊)", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The biggest and best onigiri in the world! 🍙\n\nThe owner Tony is the nicest human, and makes you feel like a regular on day one.\n\nMy favorite is the blue crab, but they have rotating specials that are so fun to try. Two onigiris are usually more than enough for a filling lunch for me. The half white rice and half Korean purple rice is so awesome and the rice is so fresh (not fridge stale like in the Asian grocery stores). And the way they wrap up the bags with string is so cool!\n\nCheck out their Instagram for up to date hours or if they've sold out for the day. (They also do fun TikTok trends 😊)", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Isabel Swafford", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103221770430202133028/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUk54rAjUnn-ay7d4BLqVLAWOuhfyNq4qFcpIeFwRYigoQJ846zhg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-18T21:30:08.402244575Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOVE1XOWxkbkU0VmpnM1pGUjNUa0ZVTTBoUVprRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tOVE1XOWxkbkU0VmpnM1pGUjNUa0ZVTTBoUVprRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3000fe7b0a1:0xbdc0bff616ef6394"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNMWVYUklMVEUyVlhWTmVuQjZSM1F5WkRWUFprRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Walked from the convention center to try this onigiri and it was definitely worth the walk in 80 degree weather. Onigiri was delicious! Ill definitely be coming back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Walked from the convention center to try this onigiri and it was definitely worth the walk in 80 degree weather. Onigiri was delicious! Ill definitely be coming back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Megan Kelly", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101391041526944491712/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVtYQf2hwSgI0e36tdy_2rvnFZh58SOtiaGuGMn3zUDO1q_mjcGBA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-20T23:19:04.822192684Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNMWVYUklMVEUyVlhWTmVuQjZSM1F5WkRWUFprRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pNMWVYUklMVEUyVlhWTmVuQjZSM1F5WkRWUFprRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3000fe7b0a1:0xbdc0bff616ef6394"}, {"name": "places/ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TFlXNWlWVWhSYW5oU1lYa3lTbVJ6Y21Sa2MwRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I’ve never been more blown away by an onigiri but this was crazy. You could taste the freshness of the blue crab and I loved how they used both rice to change up the texture. The seaweed was so crispy from the first bite. We were talking to another person in line and he had said he was only waiting just for the sauce. Sounded weird to me until I tasted it. Amazing and such a unique wasabi sauce!\n\nWaited around 15 minutes in line but once you get to the front, he makes you feel so special and welcomed.\n\nMy brother and I already trying to make plans for the next time we can come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’ve never been more blown away by an onigiri but this was crazy. You could taste the freshness of the blue crab and I loved how they used both rice to change up the texture. The seaweed was so crispy from the first bite. We were talking to another person in line and he had said he was only waiting just for the sauce. Sounded weird to me until I tasted it. Amazing and such a unique wasabi sauce!\n\nWaited around 15 minutes in line but once you get to the front, he makes you feel so special and welcomed.\n\nMy brother and I already trying to make plans for the next time we can come back!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Alison Li", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/116785201584724592395/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocIUqspU5ta4D8NoNwtcID7S-CJ_TMenQpcxepV_ELugHLuvXUud=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba5"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-12T21:51:15.541407150Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TFlXNWlWVWhSYW5oU1lYa3lTbVJ6Y21Sa2MwRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2s5TFlXNWlWVWhSYW5oU1lYa3lTbVJ6Y21Sa2MwRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c3000fe7b0a1:0xbdc0bff616ef6394"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJobDnDwDDwoARlGPvFva_wL0/photos/AWCwydjsPFWBICNRhsBBibA9YoCfzeBmkJJK7m_uXVwgHjLt78EnzQ0GgVGH_Fb_rJ43B95WkiPbREFxb8theu6oDveTFaJvrsPjSkndHWTkNg0ypIpf8hwTruwKPOo26AS22T_-k0ujIrjsHclqyJwW61kZ61QB_XUEyTODuxxd